pageContext.claim: “They're showing this sea of people, 25,000 people, they're, they're showing it's like a sea.”
pageContext.analysis: Local media reports said "thousands of people" greeted Trump at this Michigan rally. Photos and videos make it clear the total is far below 25,000. "The rally at Oakland County International Airport in Waterford Township attracted over 7,000 people, most not wearing masks," The Oakland Press said.
